window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I believe all media should be experienced spoiler-free. Going in blind delivers the best experiences. But for those of you who would like their interests piqued, here's a two-sentence description and a short excerpt for you to taste.</p> <p>Follow Peter and Fi as they work together, each searching for something uniquely special to them through the four kingdoms of their known world. It’s a tale of fantastical beasts, peculiar characters, remarkable settings, and strange powers just waiting to be explored.&nbsp;</p> <p>\"She emerged within a dark sea of green, shielding her eyes against the crescent moon’s pale blaze. The twinkling stars hummed softly, discordant against the chattering birds below. The lush leaves rippled in the breeze, tempting Fi to dip her toes in for a swim. The wind blew at her back, and she turned east to face it. The fresh air carried the salty spray of the Shimmering Sea. Although she could not see it, she knew it was right there. Her ears caught the distant waves crashing against the shore. <i>One last step</i>, she thought.\"</p>"; 
